        Code examples for {{.ServiceEntity.Short}} using &AWS; SDKs
        {{$title_abbrev}}


Code examples that show how to use {{.ServiceEntity.Short}} with an &AWS; SDK.



The following code examples show how to use {{.ServiceEntity.Short}} with an &AWS; software development kit (SDK).
        {{.ServiceEntity.Caveat}}


The examples are divided into the following categories:
        {{- if $actions.Examples}}

            Actions

Code excerpts that show you how to call individual service functions.

        {{- end}}
        {{- if $scenarios.Examples}}

            Scenarios

Code examples that show you how to accomplish a specific task by calling multiple
                functions within the same service.

        {{- end }}
        {{- if $cross_service.Examples}}

            Cross-service examples

Sample applications that work across multiple &AWS-services;.

        {{- end }}


For a complete list of &AWS; SDK developer guides and code examples, see
        .
        This topic also includes information about getting started and details about previous SDK versions.

